name: 3richZann
description:
I needed an Erich Zann (known from Lovecraft's story - The Music of Erich Zann) for some of my projects. So here we are.
Trained on SD 1.5 with 25 handpicked images I've generated with Deliberate V2, which means no real world likeness has been used.

Works well with realistic and general models. I also recommend to use the Detail Tweaker LoRA to add even more wrinkles.
